text: Don Telfer (born 19 May 1961) is a Canadian rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Calgary
